    <body>
        <%- include('../partial/mainpageheader1')%>

            <div class="container mt-5">
                <div class="alert alert-warning text-center">
                    <h4>⚠️ Account Deactivation Warning ⚠️</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Dear [Username],</h5>
                        <p>
                            Before you proceed with deactivating your VCLT account, please take a moment to consider
                            the following:
                        </p>
                        <ol>
                            <li><strong>Data Loss:</strong> Deactivating your account will permanently remove your
                                profile and associated data, including your call history, connections and querries.
                                This data cannot be recovered.</li>
                            <li><strong>Lost Access:</strong> You will no longer to access your VCLT account and any
                                associated features. If you change your mind, you will need to create a new account
                                from scratch.</li>
                            <li><strong>No Notifications:</strong> You won't receive any updates, notifications, or
                                messages from VCLT after deactivating your account.</li>
                        </ol>
                        <p>If you still wish to proceed, follow these steps:</p>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Log in to your VCLT account.</li>
                            <li>Go to your "Manage Account".</li>
                            <li>Select the "Deactivate Account" option.</li>
                            <li>Follow the on-screen instructions to confirm your decision.</li>
                        </ol>
                        <p>Please make sure to download any data or content you wish to keep before deactivating
                            your account. If you have any concerns or questions, don't hesitate to contact our
                            support team at <a href="mailto:support@email.com">[support@email.com]</a>.</p>
                        <p>Remember, deactivating your account is a permanent action. We hope to see you again in
                            the future if you choose to return.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center mt-4">
                    <a href="/deactivate" class="btn btn-danger">Deactivate Your Account</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <footer>
                <div class="container-fluid mt-5">
                    <footer class="text-center text-lg-start text-black" style="background-color: whitesmoke">
                        <div class="container p-4 pb-0">
